\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11291,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/09\/allah-punish-entire-nation\/","url_meta":{"origin":3009,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Punishment: Allah punishes entire nation, resurrects them as individuals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Allah intends to punish a people, the punishment afflicts everyone among them. Then, they are resurrected according to their deeds.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7108, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2879 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33258,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/two-inevitabilities-of-life\/","url_meta":{"origin":3009,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: What are two inevitabilities of life?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the two inevitabilities?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWhoever dies without associating anything with Allah will enter Paradise, and whoever dies associating anything with Allah will enter Hellfire.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40395,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/hates-to-meet-haters\/","url_meta":{"origin":3009,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: Allah hates to meet His haters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever loves to meet Allah, Allah loves to meet him. Whoever hates to meet Allah, Allah is averse to meet him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2683 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u062a\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38214,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/08\/ibn-masud-husn-al-thann\/","url_meta":{"origin":3009,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Optimism: Best virtue to have good assumptions about Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Khaythamah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cBy the One besides whom there is no God, a believing servant is not given anything better than good thoughts about